    "If you conclude that the price of an asset will rise within a specified period then open a CALL binary option. Alternatively, if you think that the price of an asset is set to drop then activate a PUT binary option.": "如果你的结论是资产的价格将在指定期间内上升然后打开一个买涨二元期权。另外，如果你认为资产的价格设定为下降然后激活买跌二元期权。",
