    "GOOGLE (US)": "谷歌公司",
    "Google Inc. is an American public corporation, earning revenue from advertising related to its Internet search, e-mail, online mapping, office productivity, social networking, etc. Google has also developed an open source web browser and a mobile operating system. As of March 31, 2009 (2009-03-31), the company has 19,786 full-time employees. The company is running millions of servers worldwide, which process hundreds of millions of search requests each day.": "谷歌公司是美国的公众公司，从收入与它的互联网搜索，电子邮件，在线地图，办公效率，社交网络等的广告收入谷歌还开发了一个开源Web浏览器和移动操作系统。",
