    "Listed on the New York Stock Exchange (NYSE), Alibaba group is a Chinese ecommerce company that operates as a holding firm. Via the web, the company provides products and services on a worldwide scale.": "上市在纽约证券交易所（NYSE），阿里巴巴集团是，作为一个控股公司经营一家中国电子商务公司。通过网络，公司提供在全球范围内的产品和服务。",
