    "TADAWUL (SAUDI STOCK EXCHANGE)": "TADAWUL (沙特证券交易所)",
    "Saudi Stock Exchange or Tadawul is the only stock exchange in Saudi Arabia. The Capital Market Authority supervises the exchange. The Tadawul All-Share Index (TASI) reached its highest point at 20,634.86 on 25 February 2006 . It lists 115 publicly traded companies (as of April 30th 2008).": "沙特证券交易所或者说Tadawul是沙特唯一的证券交易所，由资本市场管理局监督交易。 Tadawul全股指数（TASI）在2006年2月25日达到20634.86的最高点。到2008年4月30日止，有115家公开上市交易的公司。",
